## Unique CinC Device Locations
Creating this early on helps to:
	•	Know how many distinct sensors you have.
	•	Match CinC sensors to EPA sites by distance.
	•	Catch duplicate locations or errors in coordinates early.
```{r}
# Step: Create unique table of CinC device locations
